\fs34 Refreshing Key Information\

\fs24 As more people sign each other's keys, building up the Web Of Trust, they submit their updates to Key Servers. In order to make sure you have an up-to-date key for a Contact, you can refresh the key from the Key Server. \
\
If you open the detailed key info pane for a contact, you can press the Refresh button to contact the key server and update the key.\
\
